  "body": "*Type*: Improvement\r\n\r\nThere is currently no way a user can remove their private and public key pairs from the device after\r\ncreating or recovering their account on the device without uninstalling Status. As it's possible to have multiple accounts, it's recommended to provide an option to delete them together with all data and key pairs.\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n- add option to delete an account and make sure all artifacts fo that account are deleted as well",
